    <h1> THE STORY</h1>

     <p> The PURGATORNEY is the latest in godly entertainment, created as a way to ethically enjoy the antics of mortals without interfering with major historical events. Gods of all and any power level are able to participate by choosing a deceased champion (that's you!) and sposnoring their connection to the purgatourney! </p>

     <h1>THE SETTING</h1>
     <p> The ever-shifting island of Aria is a beautiful location for the match! Filled to the brim with different biomes, there is much room for exploration and discovery. Please do not attempt to leave the island. </p>

